name: SFError.Code
desc: Messages that describe a content blocker or Safari app extension error.

items.name: case loadingInterrupted
items.desc: There was an error loading the content blocker extension.

items.name: case noAttachmentFound
items.desc: The Content Blocker extension returned an NSExtensionItem that did not include an attachment.

items.name: case noExtensionFound
items.desc: A Content Blocker or Safari app extension with the specified bundle identifier was not found, or the bundle identifier specified an extension that was not owned by you.
